Company description: ADEO is a leading international company in the home improvement and DIY sector, recognized as the largest in Europe and the third largest globally, with sales reaching ‚Ç¨30.7 billion in 2023. Operating a network of over 1,000 stores and online platforms across 20 countries, ADEO provides innovative solutions for home improvement projects, catering to both individual consumers and professionals. The company's mission, "We make home a positive place to live," reflects its commitment to enhancing the quality of life through sustainable and accessible products and services. ADEO emphasizes sustainability and energy efficiency, focusing on responsible sourcing, waste reduction, and the promotion of second-hand goods as part of its commitment to a circular economy. The company collaborates with various partners, including the Solar Impulse Foundation, to develop eco-friendly solutions, while its brands, such as Leroy Merlin and Bricoman, integrate technology to optimize energy consumption in homes. With a workforce of 110,000 employees, ADEO fosters a culture of empowerment, inclusivity, and continuous learning, ensuring that its employees are well-equipped to meet the evolving needs of the market. ADEO serves a diverse clientele, including DIY enthusiasts, professional contractors, and various non-profit organizations, while actively engaging with local communities to promote environmental awareness and social responsibility. The company's vision encompasses a commitment to reducing its carbon footprint and promoting sustainable living, aligning with global sustainability goals to create a positive impact on both homes and the planet. Through initiatives like the ADEO Solidarity Fund, the company supports employees and their families facing difficult situations, reinforcing its dedication to community engagement. By prioritizing ethical practices and collaboration with suppliers and local artisans, ADEO aims to democratize access to quality habitat solutions, ensuring that its offerings are beneficial for both customers and the environment.

Company description: Castorama is a leading home improvement retailer specializing in a comprehensive range of DIY products, home renovation materials, and gardening supplies. The company is dedicated to empowering customers to create and enhance their living spaces by providing high-quality tools, building materials, and expert advice. With a mission to make home improvement accessible to everyone, Castorama aims to inspire creativity and innovation in home projects while fostering a culture of sustainability. The company serves a diverse clientele, including homeowners, DIY enthusiasts, professional contractors, and interior designers, ensuring that it meets the varied needs of its customers. Its target market includes individuals looking to undertake personal renovation projects, as well as professionals in the construction and landscaping industries seeking reliable materials for larger jobs. With over 50 years of experience in the industry, Castorama is committed to providing exceptional customer service and tailored solutions, including installation and project planning services. The brand's vision includes a focus on reducing its carbon footprint and promoting eco-friendly practices, making it a trusted partner for all home improvement needs. Through its extensive product offerings and dedication to quality, Castorama continues to be a vital player in the home improvement sector, inspiring customers to transform their homes into reflections of their individual styles and functionalities.

Company description: ManoMano is a leading French e-commerce platform that specializes in DIY, home improvement, and gardening products. The company is dedicated to empowering both professionals and individual consumers by offering a vast selection of high-quality tools, materials, and home decor items. With a mission to make home improvement accessible and enjoyable, ManoMano serves over 7 million customers, including DIY enthusiasts and professional contractors. The platform simplifies the shopping experience by providing features such as free delivery and returns for up to 100 days, ensuring customer satisfaction and convenience. ManoMano collaborates with a diverse range of partners, including recognized brands and specialized vendors, to guarantee a wide array of products that meet various needs and preferences. The company emphasizes innovation and user experience, striving to create a seamless online shopping environment. Its vision is to become the go-to destination for all home and garden needs, fostering a vibrant community of passionate DIYers and home improvement aficionados. By focusing on quality, affordability, and exceptional service, ManoMano aims to solidify its position as the leader in the European online DIY market.
